1
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,410
♪The autumn wind slips in,
never asking when I'll return♪

2
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,170
♪Before the mirror,
I comb my hair, lips parted just so♪

3
00:00:28,270 --> 00:00:30,670
♪An old melody plays faintly,
perhaps the answer to this life♪

4
00:00:30,670 --> 00:00:33,780
♪If fate leaves any trace at all♪

5
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,160
♪Wild geese disappear in the woods,
flowers wither at dusk♪

6
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:41,780
♪How cruel the moonlight flooding
the empty tower, wine growing cold♪

7
00:00:42,140 --> 00:00:44,530
♪Long dreams and night rain
tearing through the heart of Luoyang♪

8
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:48,380
♪Who still rides forth
to keep a vow long left behind?♪

9
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,410
♪Paint the love and the hate♪

10
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:55,040
♪With gentle strokes of ink,
like a lone wild goose flying far away♪

11
00:00:55,810 --> 00:00:57,960
♪Frost and snow to sketch memories,
drawn taut like a bow♪

12
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,550
♪One arrow dyed in deepest red♪

13
00:00:59,550 --> 00:01:03,230
♪The bitter chill within my heart♪

14
00:01:03,890 --> 00:01:06,520
♪The sorrow falling between your brows♪

15
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Scalding memories lodged in my throat♪

16
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,290
♪Burning away the warmth we once shared♪

17
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:13,800
♪I would fade away
with the candle's shadow♪

18
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,700
♪Sever the ties and stay behind alone♪

19
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:18,340
♪Let you go♪

20
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,240
♪Your sorrow lingers as you glance back♪

21
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,150
♪This longing has already worn me thin♪

22
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,460
♪We once vowed to grow old together♪

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,050
♪But if fate bears no guilt, then why♪

24
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:33,460
♪Does it play this song of tears
for me alone?♪

25
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,580
=Destiny of Love=
(Adapted from Lin Nan's novel, Destiny of Love.)

26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episode 23=

27
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:45,830
Forget it.

28
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:48,288
Your wedding with Manman is approaching

29
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:50,300
and here's a reminder for you.

30
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:52,866
Just say it, Mr. Qiao.

31
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:55,300
As her father,

32
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:57,830
I only hope
that you can treat Manman well.

33
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:03,550
If she ever makes you upset,

34
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:06,311
you can either get rid of her
or file a divorce.

35
00:02:06,830 --> 00:02:09,700
However, if you dare hurt her,

36
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:13,230
no matter if you're Fu Chengjin
or Prince Jin,

37
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,844
I will not let you get away with it.

38
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,288
Do you understand?

39
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:20,266
Don't worry, Mr. Qiao.

40
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:23,510
I will remember your words.

41
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:28,740
All right, you should go now.

42
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:31,688
Sure, Mr. Qiao.

43
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:39,580
Dad.

44
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:49,400
What's the matter, Dad?

45
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:05,270
Open it.

46
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:13,460
Wait...

47
00:03:14,420 --> 00:03:14,700
Wait...

48
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,133
That's a lot of money.

49
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,270
Well,

50
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:19,420
I've saved up

51
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,420
nearly my whole life.

52
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:23,533
Originally, I... I planned
to leave part of it

53
00:03:23,555 --> 00:03:24,466
for Qiao Manman.

54
00:03:24,488 --> 00:03:25,550
But now that Manman

55
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:26,955
has found herself a good husband.

56
00:03:26,955 --> 00:03:27,688
Thus,

57
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:29,620
I'm leaving it all to you.

58
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,270
You will use it for your wedding.

59
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:34,044
No, wait...

60
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:35,580
I know.

61
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,790
I know you've got your pride.

62
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:39,230
But with this money,

63
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:41,990
you and Aliya can finally
live a happy life together.

64
00:03:42,133 --> 00:03:42,888
Isn't that right?

65
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:45,230
Dad, I can't take this money.

66
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,333
You've worked your whole life
to save it.

67
00:03:47,355 --> 00:03:48,590
What do you mean you can't take it?

68
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,510
Isn't my money

69
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:50,830
yours too?

70
00:03:51,270 --> 00:03:52,270
If you don't take it,

71
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:53,900
I won't be at ease.

72
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:03,422
Mo.

73
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:07,000
You've really
made something of yourself.

74
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,270
Time sure flies,

75
00:04:10,510 --> 00:04:11,420
doesn't it?

76
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:13,270
In the blink of an eye,

77
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:15,180
you've grown up.

78
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,820
And now you're getting married.

79
00:04:21,550 --> 00:04:22,300
It makes me happy.

80
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:24,420
And your late mother...

81
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:32,470
She'll be happy for you too.

82
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:36,670
Dad, don't say that.

83
00:04:36,866 --> 00:04:38,890
When you say things like that,
it makes me sad too.

84
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:41,550
Don't be sad, Dad.

85
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:43,230
I'm not sad.

86
00:04:43,866 --> 00:04:44,955
I just worry about this.

87
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:47,060
If something happens bad to me

88
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:49,177
I owe your late mother an explanation

89
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,860
when I meet her in heaven.

90
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:52,260
Dad, what are you saying?

91
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,990
You always call yourself tough.

92
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:55,420
You said you'd live to 180.

93
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:56,860
Fine...

94
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:59,820
Cut back on reading and get some rest.

95
00:04:59,888 --> 00:05:01,222
All right, I'm off now.

96
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:05,420
Well...

97
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,060
Use this money

98
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,910
wisely.

99
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,533
Only spend it where it really counts.

100
00:05:26,777 --> 00:05:28,260
That was such a nice nap.

101
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:32,710
Here, time to eat.

102
00:05:33,030 --> 00:05:33,350
Sure.

103
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:38,755
Where's Yuetao?

104
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:40,620
Don't even ask.

105
00:05:40,777 --> 00:05:43,177
Yuetao was worried her embroidery
wouldn't be good enough.

106
00:05:43,177 --> 00:05:44,533
She worked on it all night.

107
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,600
Now she's caught a cold.

108
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:47,180
She's still sewing out front.

109
00:05:47,422 --> 00:05:49,533
No matter what I said,
she wouldn't stop.

110
00:05:51,110 --> 00:05:52,790
No way, I've got to go check on her.

111
00:05:53,030 --> 00:05:54,200
You eat on your own.

112
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:54,940
Wait...

113
00:06:00,105 --> 00:06:03,488
(Sun Rises, Moon Endures)

114
00:06:09,470 --> 00:06:09,990
Yuetao.

115
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:10,820
Yuetao.

116
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:13,860
Get some rest. Stop it already.

117
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:14,550
Be gentle.

118
00:06:15,466 --> 00:06:16,955
This double-sided embroidery

119
00:06:17,030 --> 00:06:18,940
is fragile and hard to stitch.

120
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,420
If you mess it up,

121
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:23,155
my whole night's work will go to waste.

122
00:06:24,670 --> 00:06:26,790
Thank you, Yuetao.

123
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:34,470
All my life,

124
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:36,820
I thought it was hard

125
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:38,150
to meet someone you truly love.

126
00:06:39,230 --> 00:06:39,820
However,

127
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,333
we both found our loved ones.

128
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:44,740
So we should hold on tight.

129
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,590
Our Yuetao here

130
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:53,155
just can't wait to get married!

131
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:55,150
All right, I get it.

132
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:57,470
I'll go propose to Jiufeng right away.

133
00:06:58,110 --> 00:06:59,940
As soon as our wedding's over,

134
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:01,350
we'll help arrange yours.

135
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:02,910
Princess Aliya...

136
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,910
Why are you blushing, Yuetao?

137
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:10,550
I... I'm not. I...

138
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:11,060
Liar.

139
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:12,620
Still denying it, huh?

140
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:14,620
Come on, tell us about it.

141
00:07:14,622 --> 00:07:16,177
When did you and Jiufeng get together?

142
00:07:16,222 --> 00:07:17,590
We didn't...

143
00:07:17,622 --> 00:07:18,777
You're really something else.

144
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,620
Drop the act already.
Just tell us already!

145
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:21,350
Come on!

146
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:21,910
No!

147
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:22,990
Say it or we'll tickle you!

148
00:07:22,990 --> 00:07:24,230
Spill it!

149
00:07:25,248 --> 00:07:30,450
(Happiness)

150
00:07:49,862 --> 00:07:51,650
(Everything Guild)

151
00:07:55,700 --> 00:08:00,160
♪The clouds stretch endlessly
across the sky♪

152
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:07,370
♪Looking down at eyes
that gaze into the distance♪

153
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:12,070
♪Time keeps moving on♪

154
00:08:12,531 --> 00:08:14,108
♪Whose footprints are left behind?♪

155
00:08:14,150 --> 00:08:16,060
First, bow to Heaven and Earth.

156
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:21,520
♪It's more than
just the courage to yearn♪

157
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:23,550
Second, bow to your parents.

158
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:27,070
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

159
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:29,694
♪Loving you is a secret♪

160
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,422
You may now bow to one another.

161
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,711
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

162
00:08:33,755 --> 00:08:36,288
♪Endlessly♪

163
00:08:38,170 --> 00:08:41,470
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

164
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:44,600
♪And gently rest♪

165
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,430
The ceremony is complete.

166
00:08:47,191 --> 00:08:51,080
♪The reason for your heart's pain♪

167
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:56,320
♪If everything could overcome
all barriers and fall in love♪

168
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:59,210
♪Even the cloud and sea
could be together♪

169
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:02,331
♪Forget how far from shore
and how dangerous it is♪

170
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:06,054
♪We can't see♪

171
00:09:06,417 --> 00:09:10,740
♪If distance can't tear us apart
and it's not hard to endure♪

172
00:09:10,768 --> 00:09:13,720
♪Our tears will stay together♪

173
00:09:13,771 --> 00:09:15,710
♪Don't forget♪

174
00:09:16,368 --> 00:09:19,340
♪The love♪

175
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:23,211
♪They could never have♪

176
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,444
At last, you're my wife.

177
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,355
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

178
00:09:44,377 --> 00:09:45,590
And you're finally my husband.

179
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:49,737
♪Loving you is a secret♪

180
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:52,873
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

181
00:09:52,874 --> 00:09:56,170
♪Endlessly♪

182
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,922
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

183
00:10:00,190 --> 00:10:00,710
Here.

184
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,430
Thank you for coming.

185
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:03,190
Thank you.

186
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:04,590
Here, let's toast you all.

187
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:05,444
We'll toast to you.

188
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:06,430
Congratulations.

189
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,070
Here. Thank you all.

190
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,260
- Thank you all.
- Thank you.

191
00:10:10,350 --> 00:10:11,740
Let me fill your cup, Mr. Ji.

192
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:12,350
Sure.

193
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,350
Great.

194
00:10:14,710 --> 00:10:15,430
Here, Qiao.

195
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:16,540
Let's drink.

196
00:10:16,860 --> 00:10:17,430
Sure.

197
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:18,540
Here, please.

198
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:20,600
♪Forget how far from shore
and how dangerous it is♪

199
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,755
Help yourself with the food.

200
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:22,310
Enjoy.

201
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:24,830
Congratulations!

202
00:10:24,950 --> 00:10:25,860
Thank you!

203
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,780
Everyone,

204
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,800
hear me out.

205
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:32,140
Don't you think something's missing?

206
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:32,900
Indeed.

207
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,745
♪Don't forget♪

208
00:10:33,830 --> 00:10:34,688
Here's my suggestion.

209
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:35,990
Shall we have the newlyweds

210
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,430
have a cross-cupped liquor?

211
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:40,310
- Sure!
- Sure!

212
00:10:40,430 --> 00:10:41,110
Come on.

213
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:43,020
Great!

214
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:45,500
Here.

215
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:53,020
- Cross-cupped liquor!
- Cross-cupped liquor!

216
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:56,345
♪They could never have♪

217
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:59,110
Give each other a hug.

218
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:00,460
(Everything Guild)
Jiufeng!

219
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:01,710
Stop it!

220
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:02,780
All right, I'll stop.

221
00:11:02,911 --> 00:11:04,044
Help yourself with the food.

222
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:06,190
Sir.

223
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:08,230
Is everything ready?

224
00:11:08,311 --> 00:11:09,888
(Yinyi Village)
Yes, it's all ready.

225
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:12,470
Yet Princess Consort Jin is in there.
I'm afraid...

226
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:15,933
Get rid of them.

227
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:16,780
Spare no one.

228
00:11:17,622 --> 00:11:18,355
Yes, sir.

229
00:11:19,442 --> 00:11:24,760
(Yinyi Village)

230
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:27,540
Thank you, Chief.

231
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:28,780
Here, let's toast to you.

232
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:31,140
(Everything Guild)
Five Leaders! Eight Horses!

233
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:32,070
Five Leaders!

234
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,070
Drink up.

235
00:11:34,470 --> 00:11:35,140
Go ahead.

236
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:35,860
Come on.

237
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:37,820
Have fortune all year round.
Good brothers they are.

238
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:38,577
- Chief.
- Chief.

239
00:11:38,590 --> 00:11:39,711
We're here to toast to you.

240
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:42,088
The groom is here to toast to me.
Of course I have to do it.

241
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:45,900
I wish you two a happy marriage.
May you give birth to a baby soon.

242
00:11:46,470 --> 00:11:47,540
- Thank you, Chief.
- Thank you, Chief.

243
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:48,500
Thank you.

244
00:11:50,260 --> 00:11:51,020
I've had mine.

245
00:11:51,990 --> 00:11:53,230
Well, this is great.

246
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:54,260
Chief.

247
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:56,350
Ji. Qiao.

248
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:59,310
It's been my honor
to attend your children's wedding.

249
00:12:00,355 --> 00:12:01,711
This is nothing but joyful.

250
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:04,710
It's just that I can't hold my liquor.

251
00:12:04,990 --> 00:12:05,470
Pardon me.

252
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:06,620
All right.

253
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:07,666
Let me see you out, then.

254
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,260
It's all right.

255
00:12:08,266 --> 00:12:08,470
Here.

256
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,070
Never mind.

257
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:09,950
Get home safe, Chief.

258
00:12:10,070 --> 00:12:10,590
Take care.

259
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:11,070
Come.

260
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:11,540
Slowly.

261
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:12,900
Take care.

262
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:13,830
You need not see me out.

263
00:12:14,110 --> 00:12:15,110
Slowly.

264
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:15,740
Drink up.

265
00:12:15,830 --> 00:12:16,590
Take care.

266
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,377
See you tomorrow.

267
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,711
- Let's toast to you.
- Thank you.

268
00:12:18,711 --> 00:12:19,140
Thank you.

269
00:12:19,190 --> 00:12:20,000
We'll toast to you.

270
00:12:20,022 --> 00:12:21,844
- Take care.
- Thank you all for coming.

271
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:23,590
Take care, Chief.

272
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:25,260
Goodbye.

273
00:12:25,470 --> 00:12:26,350
Get home safe.

274
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:27,380
There's no winner.

275
00:12:27,990 --> 00:12:29,070
Cut it out.

276
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:30,070
I'm not drunk.

277
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:35,230
Chief.

278
00:12:36,430 --> 00:12:37,900
Something's moving there.

279
00:12:38,070 --> 00:12:38,660
What's that?

