00:32:04,100 --> 00:32:04,500
Yes.

574
00:32:05,488 --> 00:32:07,333
I treated you like a close confidant.

575
00:32:08,340 --> 00:32:09,990
But even you don't care how I feel.

576
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:11,666
Your Highness.

577
00:32:11,990 --> 00:32:13,260
I did all this for your own good.

578
00:32:14,870 --> 00:32:16,311
Everyone says it's for my good.

579
00:32:16,710 --> 00:32:17,755
It's for my sake, huh?

580
00:32:18,470 --> 00:32:20,630
But who's the one who covets the throne?

581
00:32:21,230 --> 00:32:21,990
Is it you or me?

582
00:32:27,644 --> 00:32:29,288
Don't you dare threaten me with death.

583
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,950
You better stay alive.

584
00:32:32,950 --> 00:32:33,580
If not,

585
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:36,190
I'll make your life a living hell.

586
00:32:47,822 --> 00:32:49,822
No one's to approach
the Everything Guild.

587
00:32:55,314 --> 00:32:57,160
(Everything Guild)

588
00:32:58,870 --> 00:32:59,422
Your Highness.

589
00:33:00,710 --> 00:33:01,740
Why don't I go with you?

590
00:33:02,470 --> 00:33:02,870
No need.

591
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:04,780
I'll meet him alone.

592
00:33:05,910 --> 00:33:06,340
Jiufeng.

593
00:33:06,955 --> 00:33:08,400
You must protect Manman well.

594
00:33:09,311 --> 00:33:10,622
Don't worry, Your Highness.

595
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:13,670
Manman.

596
00:33:14,670 --> 00:33:16,022
You must be extra careful.

597
00:33:20,133 --> 00:33:21,266
I'll wait for your return.

598
00:33:31,020 --> 00:33:31,580
Wait for me.

599
00:33:59,088 --> 00:33:59,540
Brother.

600
00:34:00,190 --> 00:34:01,230
It's been so long.

601
00:34:01,780 --> 00:34:03,670
Today, we must catch up with each other.

602
00:34:05,577 --> 00:34:06,533
Where is Father?

603
00:34:08,060 --> 00:34:10,060
Father has been unwell these days.

604
00:34:10,790 --> 00:34:12,220
I've taken over all state affairs.

605
00:34:13,430 --> 00:34:14,430
As for our meeting today,

606
00:34:14,844 --> 00:34:16,444
let's not bother him with it.

607
00:34:17,830 --> 00:34:18,620
So, what did you

608
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:20,390
call me here for?

609
00:34:21,470 --> 00:34:22,022
Brother.

610
00:34:22,533 --> 00:34:25,422
Life in the wild must be hard
with plain food and little comfort.

611
00:34:25,844 --> 00:34:27,311
You're used to the finer things.

612
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:29,777
I was worried
you wouldn't be able to endure it.

613
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,555
I invited you over for a gathering

614
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:33,888
because I cared about you.

615
00:35:13,333 --> 00:35:17,693
♪The clouds stretch endlessly
across the sky♪

616
00:35:20,533 --> 00:35:24,933
♪Looking down at eyes
that gaze into the distance♪

617
00:35:26,493 --> 00:35:29,663
♪Time keeps moving on♪

618
00:35:30,283 --> 00:35:32,843
♪Whose footprints are left behind?♪

619
00:35:33,243 --> 00:35:39,703
♪It's more than
just the courage to yearn♪

620
00:35:41,333 --> 00:35:44,143
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

621
00:35:44,983 --> 00:35:48,063
♪Loving you is a secret♪

622
00:35:48,603 --> 00:35:51,263
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

623
00:35:51,263 --> 00:35:54,603
♪Endlessly♪

624
00:35:55,683 --> 00:35:59,133
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

625
00:35:59,513 --> 00:36:02,133
♪And gently rest♪

626
00:36:02,133 --> 00:36:09,093
♪It's to soothe the reason
for your heart's pain♪

627
00:36:09,463 --> 00:36:13,743
♪If everything could overcome
all barriers and fall in love♪

628
00:36:14,093 --> 00:36:16,613
♪Even the cloud and sea
could be together♪

629
00:36:16,823 --> 00:36:20,023
♪Forget how far from shore
and how dangerous it is♪

630
00:36:20,273 --> 00:36:23,913
♪We can't see♪

631
00:36:24,123 --> 00:36:28,453
♪If distance can't tear us apart
and it's not hard to endure♪

632
00:36:28,453 --> 00:36:31,203
♪Our tears will stay together♪

633
00:36:31,453 --> 00:36:37,093
♪Don’t forget the love♪

634
00:36:38,713 --> 00:36:42,083
♪They could never have♪
